{"tid":2004257,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"新疆監控再升級 「無感知檢測系統」已遍布各社區","createTime":"2020-05-06T10:25:56.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-08T13:55:30.000Z","uid":184679,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"57b7e75abf1384bb73dacb97b532a2fdfc280f3f","tid":2004257,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-06T10:25:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/news/600/2020/05/06/php9dn4ki.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2Fnews%2F600%2F2020%2F05%2F06%2Fphp9dn4ki.jpg&h=d9bbdc89&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n（路透）<br />\n<br />\n中國多年來持續迫害新疆人權，廣設再教育營關押數百萬少數民族。外媒披露，當局近期又加大監控力道，在當地各社區裝設「無感知檢測系統」，掌握每個家庭成員與來訪人士的完整訊息。<br />\n<br />\n長期關注中國人權問題的《寒冬》雜誌今天刊文指出，根據新疆某市政府去年底下發的官方文件，當地在「健全信息化維穩機制」的理由下，現已全面安裝無感知檢測系統，對所有居民以及外來客施以全方位監控。<br />\n<br />\n《寒冬》解釋，無感知檢測系統是指不須被監控對象主動配合，並在其無感知的情況下快速偵測與認證身分的高科技手段，透過大量生物訊息、行動規律的觀測與大數據分析，對人民身分進行判定。<br />\n<br />\n報導指出，當地所有社區安裝這套系統後，將可對進出人等進行種族、身分辨別，同時會精準紀錄所有人的行動軌跡，並標記進出時間，以利後續追查聚會動機等隱私。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3156449\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3156449&d=HVlUx73Us%2FxglV2o%2BMpWBVTAjexNHzxSh3iQmMoU3XE%3D&h=1bb48f4a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3156449&h=c60ddaf3\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3156449</a>"},{"pid":"c3d05eea466ffcd39f0cb76161aa0b4df572d419","tid":2004257,"uid":529,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-06T10:27:42.000Z","msg":"果個男人都玉樹臨風<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />?"},{"pid":"f9fb8b2380cc1f43833a1e189f03aed71f448dfb","tid":2004257,"uid":127575,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-06T10:27:59.000Z","msg":"好快到香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.g